reviewText: I love these old stories.  There are 7 cd's in total and a lot of stories on each one.  Great purchase.

My father was surprised that I found it. It was given to him as a birthday gift.  My parents are really enjoying it. He mentioned the good quality, given the age of the show. He mentioned the discussions my mother and him are having, of  the pros and cons of the show and how they compare to some of todays' shows.
